author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Again our cute Princess Necromancer becomes closer to us and the rest. 

Not only singing, also making rap. 

Talking about rap, I love Rap, but I'm not good at rap, especially in English (Because I speak Spanish) 
But at least I did a few little verses:

🎵In May of this year I meet her,
a necromancer girl who stole my heart. 
We are good friends and I join her to the party,
she sings so fine meanwhile I'm still writing :_サイリウム碧::_サイリウム紫:🎵🎶

Well... My brain was working too much, because I'm composer and songwriter. (I work with "Kousei no Onpu", but also I'm trying to give songs) 

Returning to the stream, also a Minecraft Gameplay, and a warm and good receivement to the 5th Generation. I can see Rushia's solidarity with the four girls of that generation. 
I wish one day Rushia could collab with them. 

Also talking about Rushia's calmness, again is more lovely, Taking into account the amount of "chu" (kisses) :_ハート::_きゅん: 
This, both in the normal stream and in the "Supacha Yomi Time" section. :_ちょうちょ:
